# =============================================================================
# .syncignore — SUPPLEMENTARY Safety Net for Athena-Public Sync
# =============================================================================
# STATUS: This file is now a BACKUP safety net. The primary gate is:
#   .agent/config/public_manifest.yaml (ALLOWLIST — only listed files sync)
#
# This blocklist catches anything that slips through the allowlist.
# Both mechanisms must agree before a file reaches the public repo.
#
# See: deploy.md v2.0 (Allowlist Model)
# Last updated: 2026-06-10
# =============================================================================

# Personal System Prompt (contains personal psychological data)
.framework/

# Real Session Data
.context/memories/session_logs/
.context/memories/case_studies/CS-*

# Personal Profile & Psychology
**/User_Profile*.md
**/Psychology_L1L5*.md
**/Constraints_Master.md
**/Session_Observations.md

# Private Agent State
.agent/state/
.agent/inputs/
.agent/graphrag/

# API Keys & Secrets
.env
*.key
*.pem

# Behavioral Accountability State (added 2026-06-10, R1 implementation)
**/accountability_status.json
**/trigger_log.md

